        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If true, <computeroutput>nameUiPoint</computeroutput> is relative to the center of the bounding box. Otherwise it&apos;s relative to the origin. Either way it&apos;s in model space. </para>
